These are Puzzles for 2x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: artichoke, pomegranate
City: paris, london
1. the person traveling to paris is in an even position##4
2. the person traveling to london is the person eating pomegranate##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |
| Food   | pomegranate | artichoke |
| City     | london    | paris   |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, baccarat
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, cooking
1. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4
2. the baccarat-smoker is on the left of the game-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |
| Cigar   | baccarat | game        |
| Hobby      | filmmaking  | cooking |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-3::.
2 different games are played: bridge, domino
The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, van
1. the person driving the tram is in an odd position##4
2. the person playing domino is on the left of the person playing bridge##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |
| Game   | domino    | bridge |
| Transport   | tram | van |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-4::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: camping, sudoku
City: venice, edinburgh
1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
2. the person traveling to edinburgh is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |    2     |
| Hobby   | camping      | sudoku |
| City       | venice | edinburgh    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-5::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: march, august
There 2 different types of food: cabbage, peach
1. the person eating cabbage is in an even position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in august is on the right of the person who's birthday is in march##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |       2       |
| Birthday           | march | august |
| Food   | peach    | cabbage         |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-6::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, sprite
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, iris
1. the person who growszinnia is in an even position##4
2. the person who growsiris is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |     2     |
| Beverage       | sprite | almond-milk  |
| Flower   | iris  | zinnia |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-7::.
