The people use 2 different means of transport: trike, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is in an even position##4
2. the fan of country is on the left of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2      |
| Music-Genre   | country   | pop     |
| Transport     | trike | taxi |

