.:: Puzzle 2x2-Level-4-11::.
There 2 different types of food: pepper, raspberry
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: fonseca, tiparillo
1. the person eating raspberry is in an odd position##4
2. the fonseca-smoker is on the left or right of the person eating pepper##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |
| Food   | raspberry | pepper   |
| Cigar         | fonseca | tiparillo |

